<p><br /></p>
<hr />
<h1 id="toc0"><span>第一部分：收容项目</span></h1>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/25a299389919f337b4310108562dfd65b63332c1-20031118641481142042" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/scp-2481">SCP-2481</a> - 射日</span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>这个古老的王国渴望弑神。聆听孤独的幸存者的故事。</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>历史，悲剧，被遗忘。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/bb4aa763d894517d5f3b62731efa3ef0aed0f805-470994313893854036" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/scp-2711">SCP-2711</a> - <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">定海神针</span> 如意金箍棒</span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>一个传说中的造物在湖中被发现。里面隐藏了什么惊天奥秘？</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>神话，金属，启发。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/baab0c3f70c62c2f11f3624f07157759c249050a-15806894082084001001" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/scp-2732">SCP-2732</a> - 《缢王本纪》</span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>通过一出怪诞剧解开一个国王背后失落的历史。不过要小心。</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>历史，艺术性，可怖。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><img id="pic" src="http://www.scp-wiki.net/local--files/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/2847.jpg" width="150px" alt="" class="image" /></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/scp-2847">SCP-2847</a> -禹王不死</span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>是什么样的执念让这个灵魂驻守在这铁铸的大渊之中？原因已经亡佚了吗？</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>金属，英雄，崩坏。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="clear:both"></div>
<p><br /></p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>其余展品：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-2841">SCP-2841</a> - 虺蛇的雪仇</li>
<li><a href="/scp-3610">SCP-3610</a> - 填海</li>
<li><a href="/scp-3847">SCP-3847</a> - 但愿我能与鸟交流</li>
</ul>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<h1 id="toc1"><span>第二部分：故事项目</span></h1>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/9e885ddd4961d97944f1a72bc3ddfb3ebdd87522-4702308791088238554" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/i-wrote-a-tale">我写了一篇外围</a></span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>一场与<a href="/scp-603">Megaprime</a>的绝妙经历。让它进来。你会明白大计算的需要。</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>神圣，破碎，困惑。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/726bc9449cfb48af62495e335c84263b3f50e4e3-19699348451594187418" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/he-was-blind-and-deaf-on-a-sunny-day">晴日已到，而他又聋又瞎</a></span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>你试过来到一个地方，但是你的记忆却离你而去吗？你感受过无法抵抗的痛苦和无法填补的饥饿吗？来找出到底发生了什么。</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>冰冷，饥饿，痛苦。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/ad0ec1e335d053f6b3665460fad516abd227ddcb-10154372301700496074" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/the-iron-wolf">铁狼</a></span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>&quot;<em>铁狼蛰伏于黑暗，其齿苍白而锋芒。眼望血肉之兽群，以爪猎捕肉羔羊。</em>&quot;</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>金属，野性，变形</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/2347297388b87675954b53c305177dc19095eaf0-8625273021262737469" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/the-day-of-the-dragon">大龙之日</a></span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>在另一个世界线，一切会变得不同。在龙的时代，大术士最后的想法是什么？</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>另类，反传统，神圣。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/5077a3339040be081ddf9c8e926d32614e497c20-957665100997284280" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/the-maker-and-the-beast">造主与兽</a></span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>于大渊之上，机械造主与噬神者相遇。令人着迷。</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>神圣，古老，破碎。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 190px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/82d7f1faaba6af79af4c07d8dba24355db606877-187660450790576068" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 190px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/about-the-serpent">蛇说</a></span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>过去的幸存者诉说的怪异故事。哪些是真相？哪些又仅仅是故事？</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>神话，历史，古老。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/ec21625847cd1275b753397b4cb22d6a6c4deb6a-892110487647575725" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width: 65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/of-dragons-and-serpents">龙与蛇</a></span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>向龙拜伏。向二龙拜伏。向一对龙拜伏。找出我们的父母到底是什么巨兽。</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>神圣，诗意，破碎，困境。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/5d27ed1773036990036bdaadcc35dea1a6ad5559-7137161561837843667" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width:65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/why-is-five-afraid-of-seven">何故五惧于七？</a></span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>乌云聚集于天空之上；虚空之环现于大洋之底；随后，回归虚无。</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>黑暗，空洞，虚无。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/d9aeb5090b1b76b47d773f252442ed40e22cde24-2142964026438317489" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width:65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/party-of-gods">神会</a></span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>诸神<span class="ruby">会议<span class="rt">聚会议事</span></span>。然也，此乃常事。</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>神圣，滑稽，欢乐。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/ec54cadd684bf3efbf316535e742292f29751f4f-1071519682821870089" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width:65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><a href="/and-so-the-crows-laughed">如是群鸦讪笑不止</a></span></p>
<p><strong>简介：</strong></p>
<p>带你领略人们推翻他们的<a href="/scp-701">王</a>的古老传统！另外，你可能想留意一下那些乌鸦。</p>
<p><strong>特性：</strong>诅咒，折磨，倒吊，鸟类。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
<div style="clear:both"></div>
<div style="float:left; width: 25%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
<p><iframe src="/a-sunny-day-at-the-clockwork-gallery/html/da13d620da2bd686a724fecfa39f1de5ad1cb022-4298019621613767109" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
</div>
<div style="float:right; width:65%; height: 240px; padding: 0 2%">
